[[Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike|https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/]]
"},"$:/plugins/wikilabs/info-tagmap/readme":{"title":"$:/plugins/wikilabs/info-tagmap/readme","text":"This plugin adds a new tab to the tiddler info section. It's a multi column list of all tiddler tags plus all tagged tiddlers.

This plugin doesn't change any core templates.

The code below can be copied into the tag tiddlers.

```
All tiddlers tagged: {{!!title}}

<<list-links filter:"[tag{!!title}]">>
```"}}}
